<figureCitation box="[864,937,1350,1374]" captionStart="Plate 2" captionStartId="7.[184,229,1057,1075]" captionTargetBox="[184,1068,153,1046]" captionTargetId="figure-154@7.[181,1071,153,1049]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="Plate 2: Vexillum (Protoelongata) subgen. nov. Fig. 8: Vexillum (Protoelongata) bilineatum (REEVE, 1845) comb. nov., Guam, Agat Bay, Dadi Beach, collected by night dive at 9 m. Aquarium photo by Bob Abela. Fig. 9: Vexillum (Protoelongata) cf. xerampelina (MELVILL, 1895) comb. nov., Japan, Okinawa, collected 2003. Photo by Shawn Miller. Fig. 10: Vexillum (Protoelongata) loyaltyense (HERVIER, 1897) comb. nov., Marshall Islands, Kwajalein Atoll on lagoon pinnacle at ~ 18 m, collected by night dive and photographed by Jeanette Johnson." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5846121" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5846121/files/figure.png" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">Fig. 10</figureCitation>
